    "description": "Inspired by many crafting survival games, Wispera is a procedural generated, open-world sandbox survival crafting game. Fundamentally Wispera is similar to games like Minicraft and Terraria.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2087920/extras/3a57f308dcfeeb743bca81f492d949a7.poster.avif?t=1706420582\" width=620 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2087920/extras/3a57f308dcfeeb743bca81f492d949a7.webm?t=1706420582\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2087920/extras/3a57f308dcfeeb743bca81f492d949a7.mp4?t=1706420582\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Explore the vast infinity generated world. There are plenty of opportunities to be had when searching for the perfect base location.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2087920/extras/ece21ba89764e252f629c783b9c23d60.poster.avif?t=1706420582\" width=620 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2087920/extras/ece21ba89764e252f629c783b9c23d60.webm?t=1706420582\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2087920/extras/ece21ba89764e252f629c783b9c23d60.mp4?t=1706420582\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Delve deep underground to collect rare materials. I’d recommend you be careful though, you never know what might be lurking deep in the dark.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2087920/extras/9e810a19cb582018813d7f6f2b3a13db.poster.avif?t=1706420582\" width=620 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2087920/extras/9e810a19cb582018813d7f6f2b3a13db.webm?t=1706420582\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2087920/extras/9e810a19cb582018813d7f6f2b3a13db.mp4?t=1706420582\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>After a long spelunking trip deep underground, you can use the furnace to smelt down your valuable materials. Use these newly processed materials to craft better armor, tools, and many other items!<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2087920/extras/fe5e72882ff115e2864452273e47775b.poster.avif?t=1706420582\" width=620 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2087920/extras/fe5e72882ff115e2864452273e47775b.webm?t=1706420582\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2087920/extras/fe5e72882ff115e2864452273e47775b.mp4?t=1706420582\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Wispera has been designed with a highly efficient tile based world. With the materials you collect you can build walls and floors to create any structure you desire. Among many other items to decorate and outfit your base. <br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2087920/extras/e3edd05a84fef73b5267b3a52725d3a0.poster.avif?t=1706420582\" width=620 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2087920/extras/e3edd05a84fef73b5267b3a52725d3a0.webm?t=1706420582\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2087920/extras/e3edd05a84fef73b5267b3a52725d3a0.mp4?t=1706420582\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Using your newly crafted tools and armor, fight dangerous monsters to collect rare items!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Some Key Features Include</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Sandbox survival gameplay with building mechanics.<br></li><li> A multitude of unique items to collect and craft.<br></li><li> Infinite procedural generation with multiple layers of underground depth.<br></li><li> Day and night system.<br></li><li> (Coming Soon) Crops and farming.<br></li><li> Many unique monsters to find and collect rare items from.<br></li><li> Hand written game engine made on top of LibGDX specifically for Wispera.<br></li><li> Custom shaders with dithered cloud shadows and lighting effects.<br></li><li> ...and many more!</li></ul>",
